{"tid":956200,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"喂 鄭伊健 其實短髮都唔錯喎 😄","createTime":"2018-12-26T05:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-31T11:49:58.000Z","uid":44730,"like":16,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"a256c9eca2a24d9c5a0d06405c577f687f6e67b2","tid":956200,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T05:34:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/h42tzwoH6Fw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fh42tzwoH6Fw&d=UixwtKEhE%2FTfTMM8wXbjSUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=ea1288ae\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/h42tzwoH6Fw</a><br />\n<br />\n睇吓 home alone mv，同蔡濟文一樣 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/132442_6cfb9c670d7373a86c8c5497f6205306.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F132442_6cfb9c670d7373a86c8c5497f6205306.png&h=d2164c71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"cd19876312f9a5c4c8094940ee8dd187946ca8c2","tid":956200,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T05:39:47.000Z","msg":"瀟洒可以嗎 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/04/132442_6cfb9c670d7373a86c8c5497f6205306.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F04%2F132442_6cfb9c670d7373a86c8c5497f6205306.png&h=d2164c71&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4f78d8d13f5eabe1679d5dc1b03b48a39eb956b7","tid":956200,"uid":44730,"like":21,"dislike":3,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T06:11:32.000Z","msg":"1987年《鐳射青春》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/cu3224_7941936675bf3efac9447e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2Fcu3224_7941936675bf3efac9447e.jpg&h=e33c51f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n87年伊健首次拍電視連續劇《鐳射青春》，全劇共12集，鄭伊健在劇中飾演樂隊成員，有彈bass，有唱和音！而同劇演員仲有陳潔靈、吳啟明、盧冠廷、蘇永康、黃澤鋒等等！"},{"pid":"db5e9a1aa3d14ad016153946ee3a1e8150c20642","tid":956200,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T06:11:48.000Z","msg":"1990年《月兒彎彎照九州》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/9922720e0cf3d7ca69e72d0ffa1fbe096b63a9b1_7732324445bf3c0868ba30-e1542701281180.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F9922720e0cf3d7ca69e72d0ffa1fbe096b63a9b1_7732324445bf3c0868ba30-e1542701281180.jpg&h=596b1a2c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n在1990年，松松陳松伶因演《天涯歌女》一炮而紅，之後她在20集的《月兒彎彎照九州》再擔正主演，仲大唱懷舊金曲，劇中同飾演富家少爺嘅鄭伊健相戀！"},{"pid":"48600ce085ea9bfcb9638fd77fbdec1c792b2c2c","tid":956200,"uid":44730,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T06:12:15.000Z","msg":"1992年《鍾無艷》<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://imgs.orientalsunday.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/11/000004172880_1431610737_7391090235bf3f074ee4db.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimgs.orientalsunday.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F11%2F000004172880_1431610737_7391090235bf3f074ee4db.jpg&h=6eeac531&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n1992年《鍾無艷》陳松伶飾演的鍾無艷是一位相貌醜陋但心地善良、熱心助人的現代女子李愛，因貌醜而遭男友遺棄，傷心之下，墮樓毀容，豈料卻因禍得福，手術後愛竟成絕色。愛出院，發覺父(劉江飾)、繼母(柳影虹飾)及妹(陳珮珊飾)已遷居避債，遂寄居工友傑(鄭伊健飾)鄰居美(林其欣飾)家！"},{"pid":"9556431fee239ba350fac75312d34ca5e4b588fc","tid":956200,"uid":44730,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T06:12:36.000Z","msg":"1991 男人勿近<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/26/140456_d698e92cc535b78977123879de339036.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F26%2F140456_d698e92cc535b78977123879de339036.jpg&h=52f76e24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/12/26/140610_85e0a815fcec5edbd7280557e9eaee9c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F12%2F